# PED::IS_PED_ON_MOUNT

## Summary
Checks if PedIndex is mounted

## Parameters
* **PED_INDEX** ped

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Same function call as PED::GET_MOUNT, aka just returns 0
